      "span_text": "We now discuss the issues and findings from each stage. We also mention here that the inconsistencies for the entropy values (achieving both positive and negative correlations for a given entropy measure) may be the result of many different factors, such as the noisy lexical nature of Microposts or the distributional differences between the KS and TW datasets in term of entities."
